headline: 3 Consumer Stocks We Approach with Caution
summary: The performance of consumer discretionary businesses is closely linked to economic cycles. Lately, it seems like demand trends have worked in their favor as the industry has returned 25.9% over the past six months, outpacing S&P 500 by 8.4 percentage points.
